Synopsis:
   $is_on(<nick>)

Description:
   Determines whether <nick> is currently online.

Returns:
   Returns the person's nick if they are online, or nothing if not.

History:
   This function first appeared in the "guh" script that is distributed
   with EPIC. It was written by Jeremy Nelson <jnelson@epicsol.org>.

See Also:
   ison(2)

